        <http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/languages/eng> ;
    bf:summary [ a bf:Summary ;
            rdfs:label "Durable and waterproof, with a handy slipcase and an easy-fold format, Lonely Planet's South Australia Planning Map is your essential navigation tool. This full-colour map features accompanying images and information about top attractions, itinerary suggestions, a transport guide, themed lists and practical travel tips.[Bokinfo]."@sv ] ;
